   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"It is I, Taurine the shepherd, who write to Apa Jacob the Presbyter: behold I have received fifty-five full-grown sheep being sheared-55; and twenty-six small lambs-26. [- - -] on the last of the five days of this year in the ninth indication and I, Taurine, agree. Sign of TAurine, I agree."</ab>
         </div>
